Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們將繁星摘下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We pulled the stars from the skies...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,用來裝點地球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and brought them down to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,代價是什麼呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But at what cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,當我們點亮所有的燈同時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we turned on all these lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也失去了一些寶貴的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we lost something precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,繁星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,中文翻譯 @SaltyEggPain timhal
